, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1605759}, {"id": 317446, "content": "好好的睡觉，好好的吃饭，不再熬夜", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1532902}, {"id": 317702, "content": "对一个心里有前任的人表白", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1536619}, {"id": 317447, "content": "不该在心怀山川湖海的时候去准备囿于厨房与爱，最后弄丢了他也弄丢了自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1535961}, {"id": 317703, "content": "我想撤掉每一次遗精，因为一个月4次的遗精真的好难受，对学习严重影响！！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 878753}, {"id": 317448, "content": "保持体重", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1535963}, {"id": 317704, "content": "股票", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1339372}, {"id": 317705, "content": "撤回到八年前，我会选择卸载qq", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1330931}, {"id": 317450, "content": "没有想要撤回的，即使再难受也是自己的选择。如果再选一次也不能保证会让自己更好受", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1519747}, {"id": 317706, "content": "活着", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1536655}, {"id": 317708, "content": "创造101里pick了乐华的艺人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 569811}, {"id": 317453, "content": "改了个特二的名字", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1360023}, {"id": 317709, "content": "吃了无数次烤鱼以及广州的烧庙仙鸡烤排骨。多希望并没有吃，然后就不会长这么多肉肉了。\n其实最想撤回的是，如果没有认识那个让我又爱又恨的人就好了\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1534736}, {"id": 317454, "content": "找那个汉服小姐姐要联系方式。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1535972}, {"id": 317710, "content": "遇见一个叙利亚男人，有目的的爱上了他", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1534736}, {"id": 318222, "content": "为了他放弃了学业", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1537987}, {"id": 317455, "content": "又长了10斤肉", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1506318}, {"id": 317967, "content": "加那个男生的微信好友", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1537277}, {"id": 317456, "content": "喜欢上不该喜欢的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 60, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1511651}, {"id": 317712, "content": "报考这个大学这个专业", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1536677}, {"id": 319760, "content": "炒期货", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1477944}, {"id": 318225, "content": "吃了同桌的爆米花", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 637854}, {"id": 318993, "content": "一整年都想撤回.一整年都不好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1499484}, {"id": 317458, "content": "尝试了一下《文明6》", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1420650}, {"id": 317714, "content": "投资p2p。。。应该离得远远的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1439281}, {"id": 317715, "content": "入了一家极其混乱、不做事的大厂（对就是最近传裁应届生的MT）", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 674509}, {"id": 317460, "content": "应该好好学习的……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1342416}, {"id": 317716, "content": "买了a股", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1334527}, {"id": 318228, "content": "让我考试重来一遍", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 416657}, {"id": 319508, "content": "出生", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1544007}, {"id": 317461, "content": "大学碌碌无为的4年光阴", "image": null, "praise_count": 55, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1527980}, {"id": 317717, "content": "错过前男友", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1535415}, {"id": 318229, "content": "好好练琴", "image": null, "praise_